Description: 2015 Fender Custom Shop '55 Stratocaster Relic, Limited Edition (Dirty Blonde) & custom case w/candy. Sells for $3,800 new at Sweetwater. Barely played. FCS, Limited Edition '55 Strat; near mint condition keeping in mind it's "reliced" by the Custom Shop; select, light-weight ash body with a thin nitro finish that has sunken into the beautiful ash grain; quarter sawn maple neck with 9.5″ radius; Fender Custom Shop hand-wound '55 Strat pickups.Only 6.74 lbs. The '54 U neck measures .905" at the 1st and .993" at the 12th frets and is surprisingly comfortable to play. The back is smooth and plays fast. The frets are in great shape with no wear. Every note up and down the neck rings clean and true.Limited run produced for less than two years. OHSC (as new) with embroidered Fender Custom Shop Ltd Edition logo, COA, Sweetwater Certificate and original case candy included. Key for case is missing...you can ordered another if needed.
